               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p>A. In all men, none excepted.<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Q. In what part of man is it?<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p>A. In <normalised orig="euerie" auto="true">every</normalised> part both of <normalised orig="bodie" auto="true">body</normalised><lb/>
and <normalised orig="soule" auto="true">soul</normalised>, like as a <normalised orig="Leprosie" auto="true">Leprosy</normalised> that <normalised orig="runneth" auto="true">runs</normalised><lb/>
