               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Q. <normalised orig="Shew" auto="true">Show</normalised> <normalised orig="mee" auto="true">me</normalised> how <normalised orig="euerie" auto="true">every</normalised> <normalised orig="parte" auto="true">part</normalised> of<lb/>
