               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p>A. First, in the mind there is nothing<lb/>
but ignorance and <normalised orig="blindnesse" auto="true">blindness</normalised><lb/>
concerning <normalised orig="heauenlie" auto="true">heavenly</normalised> matters. Secondly,<lb/>
